cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.SY, cs.PL 

This paper deals with Markov Decision Processes (MDPs) and their policies, which are commonly studied in the fields of artificial intelligence (AI) and machine learning (ML). Therefore, cs.AI and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves analyzing the size of MDPs and policies, which relates to data structures (cs.DS) and complexity theory (cs.SY). Finally, the paper discusses algorithms for MDPs, which falls under programming languages (cs.PL).
